%% Diagram: Cache lease coordination prevents thundering herd
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C1 as Client A (miss first)
    participant C2 as Client B (concurrent miss)
    participant MC as Memcache
    participant DB as MySQL / TAO

    C1->>MC: get(key)
    MC-->>C1: MISS + lease token L1
    Note over MC: Issue lease for key,<br/>rate-limited 1 per 10s

    C2->>MC: get(key)
    MC-->>C2: MISS + "wait" hint<br/>(no new lease)

    C1->>DB: SELECT ...
    DB-->>C1: row
    C1->>MC: set(key, value, L1)
    MC->>MC: validate L1 still active
    MC-->>C1: OK

    C2->>MC: get(key) (retry)
    MC-->>C2: HIT (value)
